reportColumnMetadata.name: Total incoming
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Total incoming
Total number of incoming calls.
Composed of: Answered by group members, Unanswered by group members, Sent to overflow number

reportColumnMetadata.name: Answered by group members
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Answered by group members
Total number of calls that have been answered by a member of the group.
Included in: Total incoming - (Answered by group members, Unanswered by group members, Sent to overflow number)

reportColumnMetadata.name: Unanswered by group members
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Unanswered by group members
Total number of calls that have not been answered by a member of the group and have not been redirected to an overflow number.
Included in: Total incoming - (Answered by group members, Unanswered by group members, Sent to overflow number)

reportColumnMetadata.name: Sent to overflow number
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Sent to overflow number
Number of calls that have been sent to an overflow number. These calls are not included in the column Abandoned by group.
Included in: Total incoming - (Answered by group members, Unanswered by group members, Sent to overflow number)

reportColumnMetadata.name: (Avg) Speed of answer
reportColumnMetadata.description:
(Avg) Speed of answer
The average wait time before being answered. This value is based on all calls that have been answered by a member of the group. Calls sent to an overflow number are not included.

reportColumnMetadata.name: (Avg) Call duration
reportColumnMetadata.description:
(Avg) Call duration
The average call duration for calls answered by a member of the group.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Call duration
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Call duration
The total call duration for calls answered by a member of the group.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Group names
reportColumnMetadata.description: The names of the groups the object or group belong to

reportColumnMetadata.name: Object identifier
reportColumnMetadata.description: The unique identifier of the object the row represents

reportColumnMetadata.name: Type
reportColumnMetadata.description: Describes if the row represent the total, a group or a an object.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Depth in hierarchy
reportColumnMetadata.description: The level of the object/group is in the hierarchy. Indicates how many parent groups the object/group has.
